{"tid":1641222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馮檢基與獲民主派支持人士區選撞區","createTime":"2019-10-09T09:23:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T09:24:34.000Z","uid":303306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"02c557d6e583e2015630ec4df7876cbe5f916216","tid":1641222,"uid":303306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:23:24.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】多個政黨及團體報名參選區議會選舉。<br />\n<br />\n實政圓桌田北辰與多名成員報名，他會角逐連任荃灣區議員。田北辰指，議會要為最大公約數發聲，支持在反修例風波平息後成立獨立調查委員會。<br />\n<br />\n另外，新民黨主席葉劉淑儀陪同多名黨員報名，她指今年選情嚴峻，擔心暴力示威影響選舉，希望選舉能和平公正舉行。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">馮檢基以無政黨身分，報名參加尖沙咀西選區，與有民主派支持的陳嘉朗撞區，馮檢基指，參選可讓選民有多一個選擇。</span></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n灣仔起步亦派出十人參選，現任灣仔區議員楊雪盈爭取連任，其他成員會挑戰灣仔建制派區議員，她指成員會簽署確認書。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=365639&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D365639%26refer%3DShare&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNluXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=48d62739\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D365639%26refer%3DShare&h=8eb87a13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=365639&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"53cf08269a58cc5073fd9a739d01d43514731667","tid":1641222,"uid":26285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:24:34.000Z","msg":"區選關愛座咩屌拿星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}